                          **** Shell Scripting Learning & Practice Journey****

This repository contains all my daily shell scripting practice files, created as part of my continuous learning and hands-on experience in scripting.

Through this project, I have worked on real-world use cases and personal project tasks, where I applied my scripting knowledge to solve practical problems. These scripts reflect my problem-solving skills, automation mindset, and command-line proficiency.

This repository also represents my Cloud and DevOps learning journey, where shell scripting plays a critical role in:

Automating routine tasks

Managing system operations

Supporting cloud infrastructure workflows

Enhancing DevOps processes

Each script in this repository is written with a focus on clarity, reusability, and best practices, and demonstrates my growing expertise in Linux, Shell scripting, Cloud, and DevOps tools.

Overall, this project serves as a complete showcase of my shell scripting journey, highlighting my dedication to learning, consistency in practice, and readiness to apply these skills in real-world Cloud and DevOps environments.
